data.description: This house is simply waiting for you to make it your home. Tucked into the middle of an established neighborhood of Old PDX, this place has history. Needs major updating and tender loving care. Sold "AS-IS with Seller to do "No Repairs". This could be your happy home as you enjoy your own SE piece of Portland. Appointment only.
